{"tid":1437130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[玩FB/IG都可以抗爭] Bye Buy Challenge罷買救港挑戰，有無得諗？","createTime":"2019-08-09T12:38:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T13:05:32.000Z","uid":23284,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"bc89472e12f976124baa79f50d5a7d6637947138","tid":1437130,"uid":23284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:38:34.000Z","msg":"經歷咗兩個月嘅時間，相信好多人都會覺得今次嘅抗爭已經到左一個樽頸位，係時候要去試下新嘅方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱啱見到有巴打發起Bye Buy Day逢星期五、日零消費行動，突然諗起幾年前Ice Bucket Challenge，靈機一觸之下，諗到可以搞個#ByeBuyChallenge嚟將罷買嘅理念落地咁推廣出去，甚至可以推到全世界都見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人暫時構想中嘅#ByeBuyChallenge：<br />\n首先發起人要post自己今日/噚日嘅開支出嚟，然後就tag幾個frd，發行人+被tag嘅人嚟緊一個禮拜都要每日用post/story嘅形式公佈自己每日開支，而個目標係每日唔可以用多個100蚊，愈低愈好。<br />\n<br />\n範例：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WcJBOGi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWcJBOGi.png&h=974a1dc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">IF WE BURN YOU BURN WITH US</span><br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論"},{"pid":"caa809bdb69a1cd09512303fee60774e134b54a7","tid":1437130,"uid":23284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:44:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05a5860133cd26b851e1825bbec9004ff814c744","tid":1437130,"uid":23284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:52:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d158e46a732b4a10846146fa7ad03d769593d3c","tid":1437130,"uid":23284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:53:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e49d0226d58d8bbbc3519fb2570b8a7e10269840","tid":1437130,"uid":23284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:55:26.000Z","msg":"<img sr